Description: An elegant instance management launcher for Neo-MoFox QQ Bot
 Neo-MoFox Launcher is a Material Design 3 style Electron application
 for managing Neo-MoFox QQ Bot instances. It provides an intuitive
 graphical interface for installing, configuring, and running bot
 instances.
